00:28:53.599 --> 00:28:59.040
are more on the correlational side than they're on the causal side. So the question is,

00:28:59.040 --> 00:29:02.560
even if you've built a predictive model, and I have a kind of a silly story about this,

00:29:02.560 --> 00:29:07.520
which I can tell, which I'm probably going to tell. You can have a predictive model,

00:29:07.520 --> 00:29:11.040
and then it can do a really good job of prediction. You can plug in the input,

00:29:11.680 --> 00:29:15.920
